HTM Admins create Asset Templates and assign them to Assets. These Asset Templates include Asset values and can include assignment of Master PMs. For more information about this process, please go to Appendix A - Classify Asset Business Process to view the flowchart and process narrative. ## User Roles and Responsibilities The audience for this training includes the following user roles: | Role | Responsibility | |-----------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

From the Start Center , select Assets from the Favorite Applications portlet. Figure 1. Select Assets from the Favorite Applications Portlet Step 2. Place the cursor in the Asset Number field and press Enter . A list of Assets displays. Review the list and select the Asset you want to assign. You may narrow the list results by entering information in one or more of the available filter fields and pressing Enter once again. Figure 2. Assets - List Tab - Step 3. Under the Details section, select the Select Value icon for the correct VA-MDNS code. (magnifying glass) to search Figure 3. Edit the VA-MDNS Code Field in the Details Section Step 4.
